{
  "stem": "13096.4",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in my camp, I never saw a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because as soon they arrive, they are-- they were put in to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when we were coming out of-- out of the-- of the wagons, and they were those Salonika, you know, Greek-speaking, Spanish-speaking people, they were advising.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't know the meaning at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They say, all the children, give it into the hands of the old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "All the children, we didn't know what it means.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It means, if a-- a mother was carrying a child, so it was certain death for the mother and the child.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because they didn't want the mother you know, to leave without the child, or the child without the mother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were put into death, both.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But if a-- a woman was carrying an older-- an-- an old woman was carrying a baby, so these Salonika people thought, the old woman shall die anyhow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So better not to carry an old person that a young baby that it will die anyhow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, you know, the-- the life of the mother would be spared for the time being.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we didn't have a single child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't see a single child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody will tell us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only-- the only thing we knew is that I don't know from what way it arrived to us, that the German were losing the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some Germans girl, you know, that they speak German, maybe they were, you know, if it's-- you know, they were listening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were giving us the hope.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It will be the soon, the-- the end.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
